column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, b, p.petror9#_r, p.dered_g, g, r, extinction_g, extinction_r, extinction_u, extinction_i, extinction_z, p.dered_r, s.z as z_spec, s.zErr, zns.nvote, zns.p_el as elliptical, zns.p_cw as spiralclock, zns.p_acw as spiralanticlock, zns.p_edge as edgeon, zns.p_dk as dontknow, zns.p_mg as merger   FROM Galaxy as p    JOIN ZooNoSpec AS zns ON p.objid = zns.objid    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid
